      info        : "This policy setting controls whether the built-in Public Firewall state is enabled or disabled.

The recommended state for this setting is: On (recommended).

If the firewall is turned off all traffic will be able to access the system, and a threat actor may be able to remotely exploit a weakness in a network service."
